Methods:
========
Methods are the set of statements that are used to perform particular task.
Methods will have
1.Method name
2.parameters
3.Return type
4.Definition or body
Types of Methods:
------------------
Methods are classified into 4 types based on whether they are accepting the parameters
and returning values or not
1.Which would not accept parameters, and would not return any value.
2.Which would accept parameters, and would not return any value.
3.Which would not accept parameters, and would return any value.
4.Which would accept parameters, and would return any value.